Reactive and Interactive extensions to Java

Packages 
Package Description
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine
The Flow Engine main classes, the Flow Engine Compiler and the Flow Engine Configuration classes.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api
The Flow Engine base API interfaces and default record classes.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.impl
Default implementations of the Flow Engine API with local and remote options.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.block
Block implementations used by the Flow Engine and runtime.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.error
Compilation error classes.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.model
The common classes between the flow-description (fd) and runtime (rt) classes.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.model.fd
The flow-description record classes and exceptions thrown when parsing a flow XML.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.model.rt
The runtime related base classes of the Flow Engine.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.test
Unit, algorithm and concept testing package.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.util
Some utility classes, including KeyStore management, String utils, Reactive4Java extensions, etc.
eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.xml.typesystem
The XML type-system related classes, the XElement parser and the SchemaParser classes.
